// About Screen About the App About App Image What is ScoreCalc? ScoreCalc is an application used to calculate individual course scores and GPA (Grade Point Average). How to calculate a course score? You just need to enter the assessment components (such as assignments, midterms, finals, etc.) along with their respective scores and weights. The app will automatically calculate the final score and display the grade index. How to calculate GPA? You just need to input the course components and the number of credits (SKS) in one semester. The app will automatically calculate the final score and display the GPA. Back Â© 2025 Bagas Aldianata.
